name: Black Lace Keyband W/ Swarovski Crystals - Green
description:
BE CUTIEFUL keybands are handmade with care. The keybands are made using very durable oilcloth that wipes clean easily and cater to the busy women in todays world. 

This keyband consists of three layers of Oil Cloth.
Layer 1: Black Lace
Layer 2: Green Gingham
Layer 3: Black polkadots with white background 

Fabric and Swarovski Crystal patterns may vary. 

Made in the U.S.A
